{"type":"question","id":11418,"title":"如何平价在法院上演的苏联笑话？","uid":3542,"topics":[506,78,96,2623,282],"contents":"(转自推特 中国文字狱事件盘点 )<br>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 安徽省东至县男子张志祥，因在微信群里说“文明社会，暴政的共匪不会长期存在”，被处拘留5日。张志祥不服，提起行政诉讼，并在庭审中辩称自己说的“共匪”是指美国共和党，说他们“支持港独、乱我中华和想要实现世界霸权”，所以是共匪，而非中共。最终，法院判定其辩解“与事实不符”，维持处罚。<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/言论自由?src=hashtag_click\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">#言论自由</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/sfYwgw0.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sfYwgw0.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/sfYwgw0.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/9DUDxEV.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9DUDxEV.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/9DUDxEV.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/6EVal0z.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6EVal0z.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/6EVal0z.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-08-01","agreeCount":17,"discussionCount":0}